<Layout
  title="Starting Your First Job in New Zealand: IRD Number, Tax Code & KiwiSaver | TakeHomePay.nz"
  description="Everything you need to know when starting your first job in NZ. How to get an IRD number, choose a tax code, enrol in KiwiSaver, and understand your first payslip."
  canonical="/guides/first-job-new-zealand/"
